e &#8211; like us &#8211; the memories and connections you\u2019ve made along the way will endure for a lifetime.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope you\u2019ll join us on our next adventure &#8211; keep your eyes peeled for news to come &#8211; and finally, as always, <em><strong>we\u2019ll see you on the battlefield\u2026<\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>During the six years since we soft-launched Dawn of Titans, the game has been enjoyed by millions of players across the globe, with billions of&hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1970,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[6],"tags":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/Anniversary.png","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1969"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1969"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1969\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1972,"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1969\/revisions\/1972"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1970"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1969"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog-dawnoftitans.github.io\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1969"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href"